question.resolution_criteria: This question resolves as “Yes” if the final seat totals following the [2026 Baden-Württemberg state election](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2026_Baden-W%C3%BCrttemberg_state_election) published before May 1, 2026 show the Alternative für Deutschland has strictly more seats than any other party. Use the official election statistics/results published by Statistisches Landesamt Baden-Württemberg on its Landtag election page: https://www.statistik-bw.de/staat-und-gesellschaft/wahlen/landtagswahl/.
question.fine_print: Use final seat allocation (including any overhang/compensatory seats) as shown in the official final result available before May 1, 2026. If two or more parties tie for most seats, resolve “No”. If the primary page does not publish seat totals by May 1, 2026, resolve using credible sources per https://www.metaculus.com/faq/#definitions. Candidate Sources: https://im.baden-wuerttemberg.de/de/land-kommunen/lebendige-demokratie/wahlen/landtagswahl-2026. (Baden-Württemberg.de)
